Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是鬼 身体真耐打
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点露出鬼那丑陋的本体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开…玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沼兰 得等到何时你才来接我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.57,0:00:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许把这颗心脏挖出丢弃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能见到你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.48,0:00:57.02,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.48,0:00:57.02,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:01:00.42,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:01:00.42,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:04.89,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:04.89,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:11.20,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乾いた風に抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:11.20,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迎面吹著乾燥的風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:17.67,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生命への 真偽を覚え 刻む想い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:17.67,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懂得了生命的真偽 銘刻於心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:21.08,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}ただ 傍に居たいと願い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:21.08,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是 祈願待在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:23.65,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人を愛し 人を憎み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:23.65,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愛過 恨過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:27.15,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲しさは  優しさ生む
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:27.15,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲傷最後化作溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:32.12,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}例え光が 消えたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:32.12,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算陷入無盡黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:36.89,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日の希望を探すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:36.89,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仍會尋覓明日希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:41.20,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃えた血の呼吸 消え寄せれば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:41.20,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃燒的血液 停止了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:46.27,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果は奇跡に変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:46.27,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果之緣 最終轉化成奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.27,0:01:48.47,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.27,0:01:48.47,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.47,0:01:50.94,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.47,0:01:50.94,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:54.68,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}闇を搔き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:54.68,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撥開黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:58.51,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手を伸ばすよ どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:58.51,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}伸手向前 追尋你到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:00.78,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:00.78,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:04.42,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}いつか 変えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:04.42,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總有一天 命運將會轉變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:09.09,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}涙の意味 無駄にはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:09.09,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要讓眼淚白流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:13.73,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}螺旋のように 蠢く果てに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:13.73,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如螺旋一般交織騷動的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.73,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(0,400)}吠えて 交わる FATE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.73,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(0,400)}狂吠吧 交織的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時間在這種什麼蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很好的紅酒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也坐一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是不親切啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然那種地方也很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝太多的話 小狐狸們會擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.59,0:02:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想到連這種拐彎抹角的關懷也馬上要失去 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:02:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫拐彎抹角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要和他麼一起回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會覺得寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使小狐狸們還陪伴著你也會寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想我回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醉鬼說的醉話不能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種對話不要對我說 跟更可愛的女孩子說去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 有你就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不可愛又任性 還很暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我跟你一起的時候最快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濱路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個會耍嘴皮子的男人啊
